OL,5, A gang of criminals have been jailed   
OL,6, following the death of a businessman   
OL,7, who died after he tried to stop them   
OL,8, from breaking into his property.       
OL,10,FPeter Cordwell, 49, had driven to the  
OL,11,Fsite in Heywood, Rochdale, in a bid to 
OL,12,Fthwart the burglars in October 2020.   
OL,14,FBut, fearing for his life, Mr Cordwell 
OL,15,Ffled the scene before having a heart   
OL,16,Fattack and dying a short time later.   
OL,18,FFour men were jailed at Manchester     
OL,19,FCrown Court after admitting aggravated 
OL,20,Fburglary and conspiracy to burgle.     
